description.en: Token burns, Rewards, LPs and a decentralized Exchange. MoonLift Protocol is a community driven passive income generator running on Binance Smart Chain. We are dedicated to make MoonLift the one-stop place for people that want to make a passive income by offering existing and new innovative features that will maximize their profit. In this lightpaper we will go into detail and speak about the $MLTP token and the benefits for the token holders.
